Package: pkgfunfinder
Title: Find Exported Functions from R Packages Using LLMs
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Muhammad", "Fatir", "fatiryousaf@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Uses the ellmer package to interact with Ollama's llama3.2 language 
    model to generate a list of functions that might be exported by a specified 
    R package.
